snippet.title: DellFan Productions
snippet.description:
This is the official channel for Mikey/Balty Raven for your dose of logo histories, logo combos, or whatever. I am in no way associated with Dell. I am simply a fan of Dell computers (and other OEM brands).

Specs (for my Main PC):
CPU: AMD Ryzen 5 2600 @ 3.40 GHz, 6 cores
GPU: NVIDIA RTX 3060 Ti 8GB GDDR6
RAM: 32GB DDR4
HDDs: 8TB Samsung 870 QVO SSD, 500GB Samsung 860 PRO SSD

My Discord:
https://discord.gg/rXXsN2V
